data.description: HUGE PRICE REDUCTION! All offers welcomed! Make this beautiful and spacious greystone building in highly sought after HUMBOLDT PARK yours today! Perfect for owner occupant or investor. High rents in the area. Two units total, first floor unit offers living and dining room, kitchen, 3 bedrooms and 1 bath duplexed to the basement with an additional living area, 2 bedrooms and 1 bathroom making this a huge 5 bedroom 2 bath unit. Second floor unit offers living room, dining area, kitchen, 4 bedrooms and 1 bathroom. Tons of storage and laundry located in the basement. Newly built shed and 2 car garage. Seller willing to assist with closing costs!    Schedule your showing today!
